  <h1>ABOUT</h1>
    <h5 class='text-justify'>Taste the Scene is a cinematic experience that challenges your senses by inviting you to taste, smell and touch scenes of a movie.</h5>
    <!--<h5 class='text-justify'>Done in collaboration with Mathias Dahlgren, the four times Swedish Chef of the Year and winner of Bocuse d'Or provides the cuisine to take you on a culinary experience like no other.</h5>-->
    <h5 class='text-justify' id="md">The experience includes a cuisine box that contains several servings created and crafted by <a target="_blank" href="https://mdghs.se/">Mathias Dahlgren Restaurant</a>. During the movie you will eat or drink the servings at specific scenes,
    creating a cinematic journey for all your senses.</h5>
    <h5 class='text-justify'>Our movies are carefully selected so that the most innovative servings can be enjoyed alongside the most entertaining and revered films.</h5>
    <h5 class='text-justify'>This is a gastronomic experience but does not constitute a full meal.</h5>
